Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大概是梦一般的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家梦想中的科学解决一切的和平时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上所有的车和摩托 以及工厂所使用的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以从天空中获取
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了资源而产生的争端也完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是5年前所开发的示现引擎的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示现引擎被建立在相模滩中心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工岛 Blue Island上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里利用宇宙卫星向全世界传送能源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早的状态也很好啊 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 铃木婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也能清楚地看到引擎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会是一个好的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发明那座引擎的其实是我的爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是爷爷的发明品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上唯一一辆能飞的摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫它汪汪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家们都说 现在是个很好的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我非常喜欢现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢这座岛和岛上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午就会到达Blue Island
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我就很期待见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我哦 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,title
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,532)}FIRST OPERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 帮我端一下味增汤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 加了秋葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早在院子里摘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葵 秋葵 秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 去叫爷爷来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 一色健次郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁打扰我研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爷爷的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你确实是我的孙女 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经8小时57分12秒不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 能再次见到你太让我高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧抱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你们每天早上都要来一次才满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 葵要回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后我就会去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃也会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天商店有限时特价
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒子鸡蛋只要10日元！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不能放过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 也就是说不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了区区一盒鸡蛋 真是小气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我们家这么穷都是谁害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是…研究一定要用的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色谱解析装置是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 姐姐一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是电车费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱能撑到去看望妈妈那个时候吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是如果不快点吃完的话 会迟到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 已经这个时间了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽快完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Pingu02 呼叫司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前高度29000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是司令部 开始引导
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(654,570)\fad(350,0)}Blue Island联合防卫军司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请上升到方位030 高度35000米准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美军也发现了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边各国否认牵涉其中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机均被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未确认部队从雷达上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动特级警戒态势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接舰队 以此为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 下一节体育课是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中小学各班一起在操场上进行躲避球游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 下一次我一定会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 一色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 葵她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 虽然出席数有些惨不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考虑到她有病在身 而且也完成了自己的课题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权衡这些因素 你们可以一起升学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点告诉桃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优 优君出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险哦 为什么要爬到那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这家伙从巢里掉出来挂到了树枝上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 茜姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 一色？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道自己恐高的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我非常喜欢姐姐这一点 但还是很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我一个人而让你们准备直升机 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我迫不及待地想回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我们吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架最新式的倾转旋翼机搭载有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能利用Blue Island所传送能源的Energy Rain System
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证会让你享受到舒适的空中旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能见面了 等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 葵已经坐上飞往这里的飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也要赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你的意思是 敌人的目标是这里吗 总理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,572)\fad(300,0)}Blue Island 管理局局长室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 应该是恐怖分子或者是某个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了示现引擎而发动的侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 一定是人类的作为了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外还能是什么呢？局长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想说 那东西是那个男人所说的「Alone」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会启动对策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果情况发生了变化 请再次联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然7年前 没有一个人愿意倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你被迫承担起事故责任而遭到驱逐 然而
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你是正确的 一色博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的「Alone」 果然来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这一次不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们家那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 还以为会死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送给爷爷的布偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是毛啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示现回路的封装虽然成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是没能全部抵消位相转移的冲击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是意识被弹出了体外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说并没有死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在这种事怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌 我的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的方法 总有一天会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这 是那儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我呕心沥血半辈子的研究的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说 示现引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不过是研制它的过程中所诞生的副产品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 这是只有你才能使用的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}东京都新大岛特别行政区通知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}新大岛及伊豆大岛群岛 进入特别警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道三原山…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：位于伊豆大岛上的活火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是火山喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最严重的灾难将会发生在Blue Island上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Island上？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 总之先把本体装进这里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰 冰箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃 你去地下避难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是掩体炸弹也没办法摧毁这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的事 就拜托了 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经约定过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妈妈出院前 我们两会好好保护这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Island居民已经避难完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许使用导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 火力保险装置解除 敌人马上就进入视野了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被浪打到就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将高度升到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有东西在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是防卫军在攻击Alone吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Alone」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(300,0)}7年前 国立能源研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)\fad(300,0)}示现引擎实验号机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}控制楼内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代码104发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究楼设备遭到严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现已陷入失控状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 好高啊 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能往下看哦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 一定会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 我现在就过去 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的目标是示现引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示现引擎？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 但是引擎如果被破坏的话 世界就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧吧 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫舰被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 天城中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间机？为什么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间机 立即离开这片空域！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 无法控制了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！葵乘在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子会撞在引擎上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直前进的话 会有通往顶层的升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备紧急着陆！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 请做好冲击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高啊 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 我们在飞哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 茜不是怕高吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 已经不怕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的究极发明Vivid System的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid System？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人突破第二警戒线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会登陆的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拯救城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们拥有这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上唯一能够对抗Alone的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Comment: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是二叶葵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的敌人Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可怕 但是如果和茜一起的话就能战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 重叠的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:26.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保护大家

